# Command Palette - Future Improvements

## AI Suggestions Caching
- [ ] Cache AI suggestions for identical contexts
- [ ] Define cache key structure: hash of (selectedNodeType, hasTrigger, workflowShape, searchText)
- [ ] Set cache TTL (suggested: 5 minutes per session)
- [ ] Consider LRU cache with max 20 entries
- [ ] Invalidate cache on workflow structure change

